The course introduces the main topics of geological legislation in Estonia: mineral resources and mining, reclamation of mining areas, sustainable development and environmental impact assessment.Objectives/eesmärkid:  To provide an overview of geological legislation in Estonia.Learning outcomes/õpiväljund:  1. Solid knowledge on Earth Crust Act. 2. Knowledge on international environmental and mining legislation. 3. Knowledge on mineral prospecting and exploration legislation in Estonia. 4. Knowledge mining legislation in Estonia. 5. Knowledge environmental legislation in Estonia related with mining of mineral resources. 6. Knowledge on Estonian mineral resources and their quality aspects. 7. Practical knowledge on searching in Estonian geological databases.
